dvbipitools (1.5.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * consolidated/merged RET (Annex F) codebase, resulting in "dipiret" as the (edge/headend companion) server.
    Only actually joined multicasts get cached in a ring buffer (needs a mirror port),
    supports unicast and multicast RET.
  * dipisds got additional optional args to properly accounce RET services.
  * dipirec got optional client support for RET.

 -- dvbipitools authors <unspecified@example.com>  Fri, 24 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0200

